Name: FName

Name of this quality setting. This will appear in the quality dropdown list.
              The names should be unique and adequately describe the Entry. "High", "Low" etc. *
SampleRate: Sample Rate (in Hz). NOTE: A Zero value will have no effect and use the Device Rate. *
BlockRate: Block Rate (in Hz). NOTE: A Zero value will have no effect and use the Default (100)  *
